IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. GRAPHICS-CLIP-CULL.
ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
CONFIGURATION SECTION.
OBJECT-COMPUTER. VULKAN-VERTEX-SHADER.
SPECIAL-NAMES.
    GPU-POSITION IS POS
    GPU-CLIP-DISTANCE IS CLIP-DIST
    GPU-CULL-DISTANCE IS CULL-DIST.
DATA DIVISION.
INPUT SECTION.
01  IN-POS PIC V(3) LOCATION 0.
OUTPUT SECTION.
01  POS PIC V(4) IS BUILT-IN.
01  CLIP-DIST PIC V IS BUILT-IN OCCURS 2 TIMES.
01  CULL-DIST PIC V IS BUILT-IN OCCURS 1 TIMES.
PROCEDURE DIVISION.
    MAIN-LOGIC.
        MOVE 1.0 TO CLIP-DIST (0).
        MOVE 0.5 TO CLIP-DIST (1).
        MOVE 2.0 TO CULL-DIST (0).
        MOVE 1.0 TO W OF POS.
        MOVE X OF IN-POS TO X OF POS.
        MOVE Y OF IN-POS TO Y OF POS.
        MOVE Z OF IN-POS TO Z OF POS.
        GOBACK.
